attributionInfo.brokerName: Keller Williams Realty Boston-Metro | Back Bay

description: Nestled in the vibrant East Side/Broadway area of South Boston, this two family residence provides convenient access to all the attractions that make this neighborhood highly coveted. Enjoy a leisurely walk to L Street Beach and East Broadway teeming with coffee shops, taverns, retail and dining options. Public transportation is readily available, with downtown Boston, Logan Airport and major highways just minutes away. The first floor unit features a five-room, one bedroom design, while the second unit offers five rooms, two bedrooms and one bathroom plus in unit laundry-appliances are included. Both units benefit from ample storage in the unfinished yet roomy basement. As warm weather approaches, the fenced-in level yard offers a perfect setting for hosting barbecues or relaxing. This home's location and pricing make it a must-see, so be sure to schedule a viewing soon! Second floor unit has a lease until 8/31/25. Separate utilities. No Open House - see Showing Instructions.
